Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多得叫博士起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完早饭之后  要不要去哪里散散步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.05,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N31
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}印尼语早安的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  麻衣  Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  祐子  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放晴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天明明还说会下雨的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  在这种天气很好的日子里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日文的天气「天気（てんき）」与小键盘（TENKEY）谐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会忍不住把TENKEY买下来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么什么  怎么会没反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了  真是了不得啊  这些女孩儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们真的认为我会去买个小键盘吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是这样吗  那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能这个冷笑话的难易度有点高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得让大家更加容易理解才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:56.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日文的酷暑「猛暑（もうしょ）」与脱发症「脱毛症（だつもうしょう）」的\N后半部谐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气太热的话就会得脱发症！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊  好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚拟时代的中学生真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}后面名乃：等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  嘛  要是家里有得脱发症的人确实就笑不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得稍微反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来次久违的神剑出鞘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「伝家の宝刀」第二个意思就是使出绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们瞧瞧我的家传宝刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你们知道被蜈蚣袭击的人会说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:30.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日文的蜈蚣「百足（むかで）」和从正面攻过来「むかっでくる」谐音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜈蚣它从正面攻过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太让人吃惊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些女孩是怎么回事啊  都做到这个地步了还能面无表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是没有听到？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  没有听到就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蜈蚣袭击的人会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜈蚣它从正面攻过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的装傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这可是王者级别的装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是意味着这种程度的冷笑话甭想放倒她们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里退缩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里认输的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等同于辜负了她们二人的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能退！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会放弃啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地理课的预习…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日文的地理「地理（ちり）」与完美「ばっちり」的后半同音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日文的防空洞「防空壕（ぼうくうごう）」与我GO「僕ゴー（ぼくごう）」谐音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在防空洞里  我GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日文的山谷「谷（たに）」与太好了「やったに」谐音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山谷很开心  太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有擦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:33.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日文的因为「…ますから」与睫毛膏「マスカラ」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛膏！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  关键就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把X代入这个公式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以算出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.20,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,350)\fad(600,0)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:11.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}攻如棋子守如球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀  这么久都不露一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当了3个多月的幽灵部员了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你来得正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在超级闲的  你陪我玩点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩什么？  玩异口同声吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来退部的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:41.50,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,260)\fad(600,600)}爆\N米\N花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来在电影院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电影即将上映之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥总会故意咳嗽一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  那个时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上星  小菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到笹原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看到他上了往屋顶的楼梯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上开始美里就忙得不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.96,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N32
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会有一些意想不到的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蓝天中  划过云彩的是  一只右手  by笹原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是写得很好吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下笹原  你知不知道自己干了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得天气这么好  就到屋顶来构思俳句罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个啦  这个啊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道记不起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么立花美里拿着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是误会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你乱丢垃圾  我才帮你捡回来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  我不是打算丢掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不注意而掉落的罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这可不是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是手帕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  只要是你的东西就全部是垃圾啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你知道那个是我掉的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家的方位明明和我家完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还用熨斗烫过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是笨蛋吗  你可别会错意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是偶尔想考虑一下世界的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才走那条路上学的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地让你送来真是不好意思  立花美里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早上很容易掉东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己是没怎么注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样把街道弄脏了别人会很困扰的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…嘛  我帮你捡垃圾倒是没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你可别误会哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是被志愿者精神所支配着罢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  美里她还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…为什么你拿着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了丢掉它了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气的时间到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:55.10,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,250)\fad(400,800)\fs35\\shad0}日\N常\N之\N33
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神与佛都不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪排饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被关在这多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来玩单词接龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:06.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一个词就玩不下去了，「蜜柑（みかん）」最后一个假名为ん，无法再接。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:32.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美绪以为要用什么来着「なんてったっけ」的け来接
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以说一个完全不一样的词吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法动弹中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:08.19,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,350)\fad(600,600)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N6
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于只剩下我和关口两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部员少于三人的话就会被废部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么好的邀请别人入部的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这个部到底是做什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  我以为你想到邀请的方法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们其实什么都不做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.96,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,320)\fad(600,600)}S\NT\NA\NR\NT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球服会被扯掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  濑木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球服给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了我今天一个球都没进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是濑木先生退役纪念服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是拿着即将退役却一球未进的战士的球服也没价值吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为濑木先生才开始踢足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我会伺机脱下来的  好吗？  好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的生存之道！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.74,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,250)\fad(600,600)}尾\N巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗  今后也要对长辈更加尊敬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  真是一群让人头疼的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  超好玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我等我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.50,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,350)\fad(600,0)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:42.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}西之围棋  东之足球  青春的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始我只是想把围棋与足球结合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造一个全新的社团而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就建立了这个社团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我完全想不出来接下来该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:56.48,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,300)\fad(600,0)\bord15\shad0\be60\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N34
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画一个飞镖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:19:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画个三角再画正方形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  差不多该睡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  你偷吃零食了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不直视我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为也许就是不直视你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要在睡觉之前吃零食呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是博士吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么又是谁的嘴边沾了一堆碎屑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好象有点感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在装什么傻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了睡觉之前不准吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你每次都不能遵守呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为阪本说要我吃我就吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡到鼻涕泡都出来了  真是杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要转移话题！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要好好刷牙之后再回来睡觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刷过牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷过…那不是吃零食之前的事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  已经刷过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要害羞啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是牙齿只要刷一次就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不好  你不是吃了零食了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么名乃你刷了牙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好好刷过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的睡前准备可是完美无缺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你还没做好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃是机器人  才不会得蛀牙呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  那个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是会稍微得一点蛀牙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是你看  你有可能会生锈的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生锈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:21:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士我给你装个蛀牙机能好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我真的会给你装上的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么名乃  和博士一起去刷牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  虽然是刷第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚上十点了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:07.72,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(1000,0)\an8}还算过得去的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  笹原他一直都不肯认真地考虑事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是双黄蛋嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好烫好烫好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死了  热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下回的日常是第…第九话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬…敬…敬请期…好烫
