Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}现在才第一次发觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:47.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是不是坠入爱河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:50.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小时满脑子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意识不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}觉得与平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}觉\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:00.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:58.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N情\N相\N悦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:02.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  视线和他对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什么什么  这种忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路乱成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:18.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那种事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:22.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感觉都要发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急转直下的我的爱慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眨眼间  脸像着火般变得通红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怎怎怎么可能  我的手居然在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是所谓的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:37.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不不不不好了  说话咬到舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟糕的沉默  我语无伦次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想知道  你对我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:41.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}你\N对\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初恋！  在平日的上学路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
